OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDisabled people's 20-year  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffight for station access   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Disabled people have been struggling to
OL,6, use one of Wales' busiest railway      
OL,7, stations for more than 20 years.       
OL,9,FCardiff's Cathays station is the       
OL,10,Fseventh-most used in Wales yet people  
OL,11,Fwith mobility issues and wheelchair    
OL,12,Fusers cannot easily cross platforms.   
OL,14,FThe footbridge between the two         
OL,15,Fplatforms has no lift and the Transport
OL,16,Ffor Wales (TfW) website describes the  
OL,17,Fsteps as steep.                        
OL,19,FTfW said a "proposed" accessible bridge
OL,20,Fwas part of the South Wales Metro.     
